MODIFICATIONS

The original OWASP content has been transformed, consolidated, and
enriched for use as a Claude AI Skill. Specific modifications include:
- Restructuring into Claude Skill format (SKILL.md + references/)
- Consolidation from three separate repositories into one knowledge package
- Addition of platform-specific code examples (Kotlin/Swift)
- Addition of report templates, CWE mappings, regulatory mappings
- Optimization for AI processing (progressive disclosure, role-based access)
